h2_title: How to Find Bishui Golden-Eyed Beast
content: After defeating Top Takes Bottom, Bottom Takes Top and reaching the Cave Depths, continue following hte path until you reach the final Keeper's Shrine in the area called Corridor of Fire and Ice.
